Datasource.Parameter: ( SELECT geometry, type, leaf_type, leaf_cycle, area FROM osm_landusages ORDER BY area DESC ) AS data
( SELECT geometry, type FROM osm_waterways WHERE type IN ('river', 'canal') ) AS data
( SELECT geometry, type FROM osm_waterways WHERE type IN ('river', 'canal', 'stream') ) AS data
( SELECT geometry, type FROM osm_waterways WHERE type IN ('river', 'canal', 'stream', 'ditch', 'drain') ) AS data
(select geometry, type, round(st_area(geometry)) as area from osm_landusages order by area desc) as landusages
( SELECT geometry, type, name, area FROM osm_buildings ORDER BY ST_YMin(ST_Envelope(geometry)) DESC ) AS data

( SELECT geometry, type, 0 as bridge, access, render, layer, tracktype, tunnel, CASE WHEN type IN ('motorway', 'trunk') THEN 'motorway' WHEN type IN ('primary', 'secondary') THEN 'mainroad' WHEN type IN ('motorway_link', 'trunk_link', 'primary_link', 'secondary_link', 'tertiary', 'tertiary_link', 'residential', 'unclassified', 'road', 'living_street') THEN 'minorroad' WHEN type IN ('service', 'track') THEN 'service' WHEN type IN ('path', 'cycleway', 'footway', 'pedestrian', 'steps', 'bridleway') THEN 'noauto' WHEN type IN ('light_rail', 'subway', 'narrow_gauge', 'rail', 'tram') THEN 'railway' ELSE 'other' END AS stylegroup FROM ( SELECT *, '1_outline' AS render FROM osm_roads WHERE tunnel = 1 UNION ALL SELECT *, '2_line' AS render FROM osm_roads WHERE tunnel = 1 UNION ALL SELECT *, '3_inline' AS render FROM osm_roads WHERE tunnel = 1 ) AS tunnels ORDER BY layer ASC, render ASC ) AS data
( SELECT geometry FROM osm_transport_points WHERE type = 'turning_circle' ) AS data

( SELECT geometry, type, tunnel, bridge, tracktype, access, 'fill' AS render, CASE WHEN type IN ('motorway', 'trunk') THEN 'motorway' WHEN type IN ('primary', 'secondary') THEN 'mainroad' WHEN type IN ('motorway_link', 'trunk_link', 'primary_link', 'secondary_link', 'tertiary', 'tertiary_link', 'residential', 'unclassified', 'road', 'living_street') THEN 'minorroad' WHEN type IN ('service', 'track') THEN 'service' WHEN type IN ('path', 'cycleway', 'footway', 'pedestrian', 'steps', 'bridleway') THEN 'noauto' WHEN type IN ('light_rail', 'subway', 'narrow_gauge', 'rail', 'tram') THEN 'railway' ELSE 'other' END AS stylegroup FROM osm_roads WHERE bridge = 0 AND tunnel = 0 ORDER BY z_order ) AS data
( SELECT geometry FROM osm_transport_points WHERE type = 'turning_circle' ) AS data

( SELECT geometry, type, bridge, access, render, tracktype, layer, 0 as tunnel, CASE WHEN type IN ('motorway', 'trunk') THEN 'motorway' WHEN type IN ('primary', 'secondary') THEN 'mainroad' WHEN type IN ('motorway_link', 'trunk_link', 'primary_link', 'secondary_link', 'tertiary', 'tertiary_link', 'residential', 'unclassified', 'road', 'living_street') THEN 'minorroad' WHEN type IN ('service', 'track') THEN 'service' WHEN type IN ('path', 'cycleway', 'footway', 'pedestrian', 'steps', 'bridleway') THEN 'noauto' WHEN type IN ('light_rail', 'subway', 'narrow_gauge', 'rail', 'tram') THEN 'railway' ELSE 'other' END AS stylegroup FROM ( SELECT *, '1_outline' AS render FROM osm_roads WHERE bridge = 1 UNION ALL SELECT *, '2_line' AS render FROM osm_roads WHERE bridge = 1 UNION ALL SELECT *, '3_inline' AS render FROM osm_roads WHERE bridge = 1 ) as bridges ORDER BY layer ASC, render ASC ) AS data
( SELECT geometry, type, name, z_order, population FROM osm_places WHERE type IN ( 'city', 'town', 'village', 'hamlet' ) ORDER BY z_order, population DESC NULLS LAST ) AS data

( SELECT type, name, area, 'land' AS stylegroup, ST_PointOnSurface(geometry) AS geometry FROM osm_landusages WHERE name IS NOT NULL AND geometry && !bbox! AND type IN ( 'industrial', 'school', 'university' ) AND geometry && !bbox! AND ST_IsValid(geometry)
UNION ALL
SELECT type, name, area, 'water' AS stylegroup, ST_PointOnSurface(geometry) AS geometry FROM osm_waterareas WHERE name IS NOT NULL AND type in ( 'water', 'basin' ) AND geometry && !bbox! AND ST_IsValid(geometry)
UNION ALL
SELECT 'building' AS type, name, area, 'building' AS stylegroup, ST_PointOnSurface(geometry) AS geometry FROM osm_buildings WHERE name IS NOT NULL AND geometry && !bbox! AND type IN ( 'industrial', 'school', 'university' ) AND ST_IsValid(geometry)
ORDER BY area DESC ) AS data
( SELECT geometry, type, name, ref, CHAR_LENGTH(ref) AS reflen FROM osm_motorways WHERE type IN ('motorway', 'trunk') AND (name IS NOT NULL OR ref IS NOT NULL) ) AS data
( SELECT geometry, type, name FROM osm_mainroads WHERE name IS NOT NULL ) AS data
( SELECT geometry, type, name FROM osm_minorroads WHERE name IS NOT NULL ) AS data
( SELECT geometry, type, name FROM osm_waterways WHERE type IN ('canal', 'river', 'stream') AND name IS NOT NULL ) AS data
( SELECT geometry, type, name FROM osm_transport_points WHERE type='station' ) AS DATA
